messages.message:
Update:
@shaunak has a brilliant workaround that lets us have cake and eat it too!

It turns out non-admins CAN use non-beta apps, they just don't see the icon advertising it. So we can give anyone access to Annotator on prod while it's still beta.

Conclusion:
:100: down for robust testing first. Will wait util all these checklists are met. (Only reason I was looking to sneak it in is we need non-admin contractors to use Annotator to prepare OCR datasets)
